          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The   energy  distributions  of  neutrons  are",
                " compared with the evaporation theory."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRCS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A  yield curve for the photoneutrons from lead",
                " was obtained using neutron counters in paraffin  and",
                " was normalized at 23 MeV to the yield observed using",
                " nuclear emulsion.  The cross section curve for  lead",
                " was  derived  from  the yield curve and X-ray energy",
                " spectrum by means of the photon difference method."
              ]
            }
          ],
